Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.15,0:01:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.19,0:01:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.42,0:01:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也做了一些準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買了一些小巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.09,0:01:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送給了這些照顧我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.20,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果紅葉卻說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.40,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色情人節那天要以洗溫泉來做為回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就在白色情人節當天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.77,0:01:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們展開了"信步溫泉之旅"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 小透妳看 是山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.01,0:01:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.02,0:01:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 是田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.12,0:01:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 好棒啊 今天是個大晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.95,0:01:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 由希、阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.86,0:02:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆怎麼都陰陽怪氣的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾、由希 謝謝你們倆今天陪我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.47,0:02:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們倆可能還有別的事情想去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 就是沒有才會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.68,0:02:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳別瞎操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好久沒洗溫泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.49,0:02:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能一起來我也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希和阿夾都很怕冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以最喜歡溫泉了 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.19,0:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.13,0:02:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到旅館了 我們一定要盡興地玩喔 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.53,0:02:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經高興得無法自制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.40,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到情人節的回禮能和大家一起去洗溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.17,0:02:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能搭這麼奢侈的包租遊覽巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.18,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上我就好像個公主一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳是公主 那我就是王子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.79,0:03:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好像去洗溫泉都會給人這種感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好棒的旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面更棒喔 小透公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這種氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的感覺像個公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果小透妳是公主 那我就是主上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我再來接各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.23,0:03:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是老闆"狼"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是老闆娘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧 妳是不是身體不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆"狼"也是草摩家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她的身體不好 所以就住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊管理旅館一邊養身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉嚇到您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您不要太勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的身體才是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是個好心的小姐 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望紫吳少爺也一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的工作是不是很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已不是"少爺"的年紀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有兩部作品的截稿日期都到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的客人只有你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢地休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.62,0:04:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道老闆娘也是草摩家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她知道十二生肖的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道她也是十二生肖的一位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好寬敞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫各位準備了最好的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳過來 這個庭園好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.31,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～ 好美 好感動喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部有多大呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.12,0:05:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的森林和那座山全都是草摩家的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？全部都是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 全部都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.16,0:05:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定值得去走走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也有人一去散步就再也沒回來過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 笑笑就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.81,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是開玩笑啊 就是嘛 怎麼可能會有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人都被找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為草摩的搜查隊個個都是專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 還有搜查隊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 小透我說笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊..原來啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.23,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透小姐的房間就在少爺們的隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.47,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我要跟那臭由希住同一個房間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還沒有和好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.24,0:06:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 裡面有紙門 可以幫你們隔開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這間旅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少裝了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你是想跟小透一起睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 你怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以有這種想法 你這樣子想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.93,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來一定會發生事情的 到時你就後悔不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是叫人害怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的樣子才叫人害怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是我不對 我向你們道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向全世界道歉 請原諒我 原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 跟他同房就同房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 淫蕩淫蕩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的身體真的很虛弱嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位慢慢休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 終於安靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離晚餐還有一點時間 我們去泡溫泉吧 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起泡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最淫蕩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了 紅葉還小嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去洗 要去要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以太任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天來這裡不是來為難小透的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是晚上要和我一起睡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔 我還是第一次泡露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉可以游泳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在游泳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再跳一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅葉 拜託你安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 水溫如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹嘛 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小透一個人很無聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來唱歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.07,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就很像大家一起泡 一定會很快樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱..唱歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我不知道要唱什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我來唱好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下的山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.75,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.83,0:09:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙和蜥蜴在說著你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鯉魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在唱什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌 是我自己作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不能作首好聽點的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳也一起唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下的山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換妳唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下的山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.96,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.23,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙和蜥蜴在說著你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是青蛙跟蜥蜴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別唱這首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.17,0:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙和蜥蜴在說著你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～ 我快發瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下的山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙和蜥蜴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.79,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在說著你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鯉魚生魚片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.13,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有活的小鰻魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.54,0:10:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽西下的山上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.64,0:10:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙和蜥蜴在說著你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒啦 妳剛才在溫泉裡昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的溫泉很容易讓人頭暈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.72,0:11:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說這張照片嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為塑膠袋包得很緊 所以沒有弄濕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.66,0:11:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我好像給妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人怎麼可以向我道歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的溫泉容易讓人頭暈 我才應該先跟妳道歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個不稱職的老闆娘 實在是太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想挖個洞鑽進去喔 對不起 實在很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我母親 她去年過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.93,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想讓媽媽享受一下溫泉 所以就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.35,0:12:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我已經沒事了 真的很謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇哇～ 好棒的大餐喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是山中的珍味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多吃得完嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫各位盛飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妳今天是公主 這種事由我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多飯她哪吃得完…好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打我幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天小透最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 快點吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可別客氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.82,0:13:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 因為太高興反而覺得緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夾到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 多吃點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師傅堅持要跟少爺們打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.92,0:13:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爺們 好久不見 不知道料理的味道如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.02,0:13:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃到下巴都快掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！失禮了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實…實在是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天上給少爺們的料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.97,0:14:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來是打算不是很燙就是要很涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我一時的疏忽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.71,0:14:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟端出這種不熱不冷的料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.75,0:14:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我一定要切腹謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 都是我的責任 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯…是我的錯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們倆是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 他們是堂兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遺傳的力量真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫泉的氤氳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 既然難得來了 就再去泡一次露天溫泉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過要小心別再昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.92,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？容易頭暈的人專用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好貼心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.99,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 妳不會冷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.37,0:15:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕會把妳弄濕 所以請妳在那邊忍一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道水溫如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個板子是我剛才放上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又跟媽媽一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透小姐妳真體貼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我沒有機會告訴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.53,0:15:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我兒子也跟少爺們一樣是十二生肖的一員 他是猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.00,0:15:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛開始聽到妳的事時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.34,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 我真的很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有草摩以外的人知道十二生肖這個秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.11,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕我兒子和少爺們內心的創傷會更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.39,0:15:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在我為自己曾有這種想法跟妳道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是小透小姐的話那我就安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來有一天 如果妳能遇到我兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請像妳和少爺們一樣好好地跟他相處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.77,0:16:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想趕快見到你喔 小猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 老闆娘是小津的媽媽 抱歉忘記告訴妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小透妳要不要打乒乓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆根本不理我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過球只能彈一次嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣怎麼打下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是規則啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又出界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說偶而陪你玩玩也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰跟你玩這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.73,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拳頭！男人就要靠拳頭決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己說要比乒乓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這樣好了 來跟我比吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.10,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩 比吧比吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我話先說在前頭 我可不會因為妳是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就故意放水喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記了 只能彈一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒打到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就很厲害嗎 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不信就來比啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰怕誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.08,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是哪裡不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的…好好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會突然揮空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.13,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以當面笑我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要在阿夾的面前笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.64,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說我連在父母面前也不曾這麼笑過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑得好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該早點給妳的 可是一直找不到時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送妳的回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來一直下不定決心要送妳什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.54,0:19:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來想說這可能最適合妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜歡嗎？公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…是 當然喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.99,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是光榮之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.41,0:19:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子真的好像王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家有好多的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.49,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很帥的 很可愛的 很體貼的王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.63,0:19:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能這樣子渡過一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我真的是好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.77,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼美好的夜晚我一定要說出我的謝意才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是捨不得你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.09,0:20:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定要再來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也別緊靠著我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您保重身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透也是 好好保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.57,0:20:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接我們的巴士怎麼那麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和紅葉又要很久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.61,0:20:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 春天開始你要唸幾年級呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初中一年級嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.55,0:20:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天開始我就是高中一年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.92,0:20:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我要唸你們學校和阿春一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.76,0:21:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你和阿春幹嘛偷偷來報考我們學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你們嚇一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.27,0:21:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田 我想妳可能不太清楚 其實紅葉只小我們一歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和阿春同年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.44,0:21:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.88,0:21:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為他是小學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到今年春天就要在同一個學校念書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟阿春一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在是不知叫我該驚訝哪個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都驚訝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.62,0:21:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天以後的高中生涯一定會很熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送給妳的情人節回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到她會穿著這個叫我"主人"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得好興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被抓去關就好了
